metadata.name: Confirmations GET /api/v1/emails/check_confirmation with an authentication cookie when the account is confirmed returns the confirmation status successfully

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT "session_activations".* FROM "session_activations" WHERE "session_activations"."user_id" = $1 ORDER BY created_at desc OFFSET $2
